public class NearbyCoverageRequest
extends AbstractRequest<NearbyCoverageResult>
    Represents a request to retrieve nearby public transit data coverage. All setter methods return the current instance, so these calls can be chained.

    IMPORTANT: Urban Mobility Coverage Search is a Beta feature. The related classes are subject to change without notice.
